name: The Un̴k̸n̶o̷w̵n̸ Domain 1
description: The Unkown Domain" is an ongoing collection of semi-figurative and abstract surreal illustrations created using free domain original scanned artworks (CC0 licence) from French artists that range from  the 15th to the 19th century, following the principle of compositing cells and layers as textures for each piece creating a final composition made from the multiplied overlayed iterated textures of each artist original work.
